title: FBI Releases IOCs Associated with BlackCat/ALPHV Ransomware

sentences: The Federal Bureau of Investigation (FBI) has released a Flash report detailing indicators of compromise (IOCs) associated with attacks involving BlackCat/ALPHV, a Ransomware-as-a-Service that has compromised at least 60 entities worldwide.
